                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t17230710-18-defend99 t17230710-18-deflabel89"></join> to dig in the Ruins of the late Fire in <placeName id="t17230710-18-crimeloc90">Billiter Lane</placeName>
